    "3a and 4a, due to the way in which they are built, each level has its own vertical linear scale, which may vary significantly within the same plot.",
    "By construction, every level is rescaled in such a way that all levels appear to have the same height.",
    "We opted for this particular representation because these plots are designed to show the morphological evolution of the differential merger rate rather than the relative magnitude at different redshifts.",
